methods.resize:
Scales a shape by multiplying x and y coordinates by factor.

:param s: (java.awt.Shape) - shape
:param factor: (double) - size factor
:return: (java.awt.Shape) new shape equal to s resized by factor
methods.rotate:
Rotates a shape by multiplying x and y coordinates by angle radians.

:param s: (java.awt.Shape) - shape
:param angle: (double) - angle in radians
:return: (java.awt.Shape) new shape equal to s rotated by angle
